          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1379.-step-4-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the vegetables have softened, add the <strong>balsamic vinegar</strong>, <strong>chopped garlic</strong>&nbsp;and <strong>dried</strong>&nbsp;<strong>oregano</strong> and cook for 1 min or until fragrant</p>\r\n<p>Add the <strong>puy-style lentils</strong> and <strong>chicken stock</strong> and cook, covered, for 25-30 min or until the lentils are tender</p>",
